snippet.title: Puzzle Hero
snippet.description:
You must free your brother from Zalock and his evil army of vegetables! Duel with green bean monsters, pumpkins, and up to 50 other species. Collect gold and use it to shop for magical amulets, weapons, and accessories to become the Puzzle Hero.

http://www.bigfishgames.com/download-games/3680/puzzle-hero/index.html
